      • buildOneSide

        public void buildOneSide(boolean side,
                         Set<String> attributeNames,
                         double deviatAngle,
                         double deviatSum,
                         boolean noStop)
        Parameters:
        side - : the chosen side (initial or final) true is initial and false is final
        attributeNames - : the names of the attribute used for attribute continuity.
        angle - : the limit deviation angle for continuity
        somme - : the limit difference of deviation angles sum for consecutive points.
